                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 10vb: Ownership note.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 10vb: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘወልደ፡ ሚካኤል፡ አቡሁ፡ ተስፋ፡ ማርያም፡ ወስመ፡ እሙ፡ ወለተ፡ ሚካኤል፡፡</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 10vb: This book is of Wäldä Mikaˀel, his father is Täsfa Maryam and the name of his mother is Wälätta Mikaˀel.</q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 84rb: Donation note.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 84rb: ˂…˃ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ˂…˃፡ ዘወሀቦ፡ ወልደ፡ ሚካኤል፡ አቡሁ፡ ተስፋ፡ ማርያም፡ ዓመተ፡ ሚካኤል፡፡</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 84rb: [This] book is of St. Michael ˂…˃, which Wäldä Mikaˀel donated. His father is Täsfa Maryam [and his … is] ˁAmätä Mikaˀel.</q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 84va: Donation note. </locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 84va: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘመድኃኒ፡ ዓለም፡ አዲግራት፡ ዘወሀቦ፡ ዳግማዊ፡ ዘመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ወምስለ፡ ብእሲቱ፡ ዓመተ፡ ድንግል፡ ከመ፡ ይኵኖሙ፡ መርሃ፡ ለመንግስተ፡ ሰማያት፡፡</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title of the work, ግንዘት, is written in blue pen: fol. 1r.&#xD;
- Tämälläs-sign indicating the place where the omission, written in the margin, belong: fol. 58rb.&#xD;
- Corrections written interlineally: fols. 10rb, 10vb, 26ra, 38va, 71rb, 76va, 79ra.&#xD;
- Space for rubricated names left unfilled in the supplication formulas: fols. 14ra, 64v.&#xD;
- A note, probably the original ownership or donation note, has been erased from fol. 84rb.&#xD;
- A note, probably concerning donation, has been blotted out from fol. 84va.&#xD;
- Pen trial: fol. 10r.</item>
                     </list>
