                  <persName corresp="PRS0000" instant="false" full="yes">The name of the original donor has been erased from the supplication formulas and replaced with the names of Wäldä Mikaʾel, Täsfa Maryam and Wälätta Mikaʾel (e.g., fols. 14vb, 38ra, 52vb), Wäldä Yoḥannǝs (e.g., fol. 61vb), Gäbrä Ḥǝywot (e.g., fol. 62ra), Kǝnfä Mikaʾel (e.g., fol. 61va). The first three names are also mentioned in Additiones 1 and 2. &#xD;
All the names have been added by a secondary hand, in vivid scarlet.&#xD;
According to Additio 3, the Ms. was donated by Dagǝmawi Zä-Mänfäs Qǝddus and his wife ʾAmätä Dǝngǝl. Dagǝmawi Zä-Mänfäs Qǝddus might be identified with the second son of däğğazmač Säbagadis (1770-1831), Ḫagos (d. 1831). The identification is based on Additiones 1 and 2 in Ms. FBM-002. He also donated Ms. FBM-009.</persName>
